\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {5}{\ignorespaces Configuration-picker accuracy on the 87 paired problems. $^*$The deterministic alternating predictor's 64.4\% reflects a fortuitous alignment of its output sequence with the data ordering rather than a real signal; the expected accuracy of a properly random predictor is 50\%.}}{11}{table.5}\protected@file@percent }
